>Would someone be so kind as to mail me the publisher, isbn number, author
>and publisher phone number if you have it of the Applied Cryptography book
>which includes a disk of the source with it.  Bruce Scheier is the author?
The book is _Applied Cryptograhy_, by Bruce Schneier (not Scheier).  The
publisher is John Wiley & Sons, Inc., ISBN 0-471-59756-2.  List price is
$44.95, but I got mine from the book club for a lot less.

By the way, the disk doesn't come with the book (at least not the version
I got).  It is available separately for $30.

